{"tid":448481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國亞裔家長送卍字蠟燭 猶太裔要求道歉","createTime":"2017-10-26T09:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T03:33:50.000Z","uid":75969,"like":182,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"8d05ad301346629e9f0f6967769523f6bbbfd90f","tid":448481,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/10/26/4/4162611.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F4%2F4162611.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=a5260a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「卍」字在亞洲代表著吉祥。(美聯社) 朱澤人</span><br />\n<br />\n美國紐約長島納蘇郡賽奧塞(Syosset)一名亞裔家長為慶祝光明節(Diwali)，自製雕有「卍」字的紅色小蠟燭送給小孩的班上同學，不料有猶太裔家長誤認為是納粹標記「卐」，向學區投訴。<br />\n<br />\n華人家長指出，各族裔間應互相了解彼此的文化，不應該無理取鬧要校方道歉。<br />\n<br />\n來自台灣的梁太太指出，24日收到賽奧塞學區發出一封信件，內容為解釋佛教與納粹符號意涵完全不同。向其他家長詢問才發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">原來一名印度裔家長為慶祝光明節，自製蠟燭送給孩子班上同學，不過由於上面刻有「卍」字，被猶太家長一狀告上學區委員會，質疑有歧視猶太人意涵。</span><br />\n<br />\n發生此事的學校校長24日透過賽奧塞學區總監辦公室發信給家長，指出校方致力讓孩子了解與接受多元文化，目標就是建造一個能彼此包容、互相尊重異同的社會。<br />\n<br />\n19日是印度裔光明節，慶祝光明戰勝黑暗，而「卍」字代表著神聖與吉祥好運。「然而，這個符號提醒著痛苦與歷史悲劇，你的孩子班上收到禮物(一個有吉祥符號的蠟燭)是慶祝光明節的家長所給，祝福孩子快樂、開心與富裕。」<br />\n<br />\n信中最後寫著，儘管此蠟燭禮物沒想傷害任何人，校方意識到無法把這兩個符號完全分離，送此禮物給學生是個錯誤，對此表達抱歉，未來在慶祝多元文化時會更加小心。<br />\n<br />\n梁太太表示，其實「卍」字在亞洲是很常見的吉祥符號，向學區投訴的猶太家長應要先了解其他文化，假設送禮的印度家長是好意，不該直接告到學區。「這本來就是個多元族裔的社會，如果我們能先為設想對方根本不是傷害任何人，就不會把事情搞大，如今這位印度裔家長好心反而惹禍，恐怕以後也會害怕送禮給別人」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6813/2779582?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6813%2F2779582%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catebreaknews_ch2&d=j8M6UL9r%2BYhbQd%2FflA0DHv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ecffd3d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6813/2779582?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"dd8ca266fa0159c54cc37b32bcb015d180fb4bda","tid":448481,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a5495ad3d060ff49bd1c7898684793b7ddd5e3","tid":448481,"uid":26752,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:09:00.000Z","msg":"左膠又柒一獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fbe39dca8059aecd0f2b2b58459bf66b81a6c4","tid":448481,"uid":50327,"like":269,"dislike":2,"score":267,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:09:20.000Z","msg":"猶太人一向都唔融入社群<br />\n點會理你咁多"},{"pid":"310a633bb4bad37d9173247e6ce46f8244309175","tid":448481,"uid":683,"like":188,"dislike":2,"score":186,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"當冒犯左其它種族既時候：係你唔了解我地既文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當自己種族被冒犯既時候：係你唔尊重我地既文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44a201d7cd52be55e5492d759a9128d3b5d2a3a","tid":448481,"uid":82532,"like":240,"dislike":2,"score":238,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/when-finishing-a-race-is-your-passion-running-adolf-hitler.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fwhen-finishing-a-race-is-your-passion-running-adolf-hitler.jpg&h=15c7c8b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8de508431e52203f24551439be8188fa6abc774c","tid":448481,"uid":86828,"like":3,"dislike":95,"score":-92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:11:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多野唔送送個卍字俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2785e926bf876b3593a0c574508e4c23661b686","tid":448481,"uid":75969,"like":133,"dislike":0,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"咁算唔算唔尊重印度文化?<br />\n可唔可以要求返個猶太裔道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7af84e41221a41dda4bb7ae1f99f72fa22bc7c","tid":448481,"uid":17616,"like":169,"dislike":3,"score":166,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:14:39.000Z","msg":"卐 同 卍 兩隻字黎喎..."},{"pid":"607ffd870cf974942cd658e11ffa97d46a779fc1","tid":448481,"uid":80461,"like":41,"dislike":9,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"當年希特拉點解滅唔撚曬啲猶太人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef51cc3ba5ca5de9c9d2dbaf80db7c402208f48f","tid":448481,"uid":16949,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"而家猶太人連順時針逆時針都唔識分"},{"pid":"d6d7baff04182429b84c5d398e42eceabd2ebe53","tid":448481,"uid":56157,"like":232,"dislike":2,"score":230,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多野唔送送個卍字俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就痴線，卍字係印度佛教傳統符號，送嗰條友係印度人。<br />\n反而搞錯方向以為被人迫害條猶太人先痴線。<br />\n納粹係用卐唔係卍，互聯網咁撚發達查到唔查下扮哂受害人以為被人種族歧視。<br />\n事實上係佢歧視緊印度人。人地又唔係淨係送比你一個，係送比全班。"},{"pid":"1b806d68115468ef277bcf70cc018128a556be95","tid":448481,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 膠都廢事畀"},{"pid":"464e912ee30ad3275a27645c9ee9fbe35a936924","tid":448481,"uid":128568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"